index_terms: MYRTLE EDWARDS PARK DEPARTMENT OF PARKS AND RECREATION
summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting an award in connection with the condemnation of land and other property in Blocks 164 and 167 Seattle Tidelands for Park and Recreation purposes (Elliott Bay Park) under Ordinance 97678, King County Cause No. 712141, and making an appropriation from the Park Acquisition and Development Fund therefor.
